{"search_data": "BiharBihar Victim Compensation Scheme 2018 \u2013 Rs. 7 lakh for Rape & Acid Attack Victims \u0939\u093f\u0902\u0926\u0940 \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u092a\u0922\u093c\u0947\u0902Table of Contents  Bihar Victim Compensation Scheme 2018 for Rape & Acid Attack VictimsBihar Victim Compensation Scheme 2014 for Rape and Acid Attack VictimsReferencesBihar Victim Compensation Scheme 2018 for Rape & Acid Attack VictimsThe important features and highlights of this Bihar Victim Compensation (Amendment) Scheme 2018 are as follows:-Now all the Acid Attack Victims and Rape Victims will get compensation amount of Rs. 7 lakh instead of Rs. 3 lakh under Bihar Victim Compensation Scheme 2018.In case the age of victim is below 14 years, then this compensation amount can be increased by 50% over and above Rs. 7 lakh.If Acid Attack Victims have lost their 80% or more eyesight or 80% or more face has been disfigured, then there is a provision of providing Rs. 10,000 per month as compensation. This could be for the entire life or for the duration as considered appropriate by the District Crime Compensation Board.In no case, the amount being provided compensation can exceed Rs. 10,000 per month for acid attack victims.District Legal Service Authority is given the responsibility to finally take a decision on the release of compensation amount to the victims. Rest Procedures and Eligibility criteria are same as mentioned in the previous Bihar Victim Compensation Scheme, 2014.Bihar Victim Compensation Scheme 2014 for Rape and Acid Attack VictimsIn the previous Victim Compensation Scheme in Bihar, all the acid attack and rape victims are entitled for compensation amount of Rs. 3 lakh. The complete schedule is shown in the image below:-Bihar Victim Compensation Scheme 2014 This amount has now been changed to Rs. 7 lakh for both rape and acid attack victims in Bihar Victim Compensation (Amendment) Scheme 2018. All the procedures will remain same as per the previous scheme and the amendments proposed are mentioned above. To see the complete details of the previous scheme, click the link given below:- http://bslsa.bih.nic.in/PDF/schemes16/Bihar%20victim%20copm.%202014.pdfReferences\u2014 For more details, visit the official website http://bslsa.bih.nic.in/schemes.html  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}